description:
Cannadrix was founded on February 9, 2018. The company specializes in renewable energy technologies, energy-efficient construction and holistic medicine based on medical cannabis, improving the quality of everyday life, as well as the standard of care for patients whose medical needs are difficult to meet.
Thanks to cooperation with leading renewable energy companies and BIO, Cannadrix invests in the development and use of the latest green technologies from the renewable energy sector.
name: Cannadrix
